title: Official Xbox Magazine - Grand Theft Auto Game Guide - Winter 20
description:
Official Xbox Magazine - Grand Theft Auto Game Guide - Winter 2013

100 Pages | True PDF | English | 27 MB 


Trouble taps on your window again with this next chapter in the Grand Theft Auto universe, set in the city of Los Santos and its surrounding hills, countryside and beaches. A bold new direction in open-world freedom, storytelling, Grand Theft Auto V focuses on the pursuit of the almighty dollar in a re-imagined, present-day Southern California.
